@startuml
title TAF Lab - Use Case Diagram

left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false

actor "QA Engineer" as QA
actor "CI Runner" as CI
actor "Automation Exercise UI" as WebSUT
actor "Automation Exercise API" as ApiSUT

rectangle "Framework Execution Use Cases" {
  usecase "Run Smoke Suite" as UC1
  usecase "Run UI Regression Suite" as UC2
  usecase "Run API Regression Suite" as UC3
  usecase "Run Full Regression Suite" as UC4
  usecase "Load Execution Config" as UC5
  usecase "Provision Browser Session" as UC6
  usecase "Provision API Client" as UC7
  usecase "Capture Evidence\n(Allure + Surefire)" as UC8
  usecase "Capture Screenshot on UI Failure" as UC9
}

rectangle "Tested Business Scenarios" {
  usecase "Validate Home Page Smoke" as UC10
  usecase "Validate Products Catalog API" as UC11
  usecase "Register New User\n(Happy Path)" as UC12
  usecase "Login With Valid Seeded User" as UC13
  usecase "Search Products Via UI" as UC14
  usecase "Reach Checkout After API/UI Setup" as UC15
}

QA --> UC1
QA --> UC2
QA --> UC3
QA --> UC4
CI --> UC1
CI --> UC3
CI --> UC4

UC1 .> UC5 : <<include>>
UC1 .> UC6 : <<include>>
UC1 .> UC8 : <<include>>
UC1 .> UC9 : <<extend>>
UC1 .> UC10 : <<include>>

UC2 .> UC5 : <<include>>
UC2 .> UC6 : <<include>>
UC2 .> UC7 : <<include>>
UC2 .> UC8 : <<include>>
UC2 .> UC9 : <<extend>>
UC2 .> UC12 : <<include>>
UC2 .> UC13 : <<include>>
UC2 .> UC14 : <<include>>

UC3 .> UC5 : <<include>>
UC3 .> UC7 : <<include>>
UC3 .> UC8 : <<include>>
UC3 .> UC11 : <<include>>

UC4 .> UC1 : <<include>>
UC4 .> UC2 : <<include>>
UC4 .> UC3 : <<include>>
UC4 .> UC15 : <<include>>

WebSUT --> UC10
WebSUT --> UC12
WebSUT --> UC13
WebSUT --> UC14
WebSUT --> UC15
ApiSUT --> UC11
ApiSUT --> UC15

note right of UC15
Target V1 business scenario.
Current repository keeps the checkout
test class as an explicit skipped placeholder.
end note

@enduml
